data.description: Bring your imagination. This property provides the most tranquil setting. Enjoy all nature has to offer on your private 6.2 acres. This 1995 manufactured home has plenty of space, with well-sized bedrooms and two full baths. The kitchen provides a large eating area. The front deck provides plenty of room for entertainment. There is a 20’X30” metal shop with a metal roof that includes a 10’X10’ backroom with a ½ bath. The property also boasts a woodshed, gazebo, play equipment and a chicken coop. There are great recreational areas nearby, and only a short drive to the town of Sedro-Wooley and all the conveniences. Welcome Home!
